      <title>EQT 支持的 Waystar 考虑将 IPO 定价在中档附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/eqt-backed-waystar-is-said-to-weigh-pricing-ipo-around-mid-range</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，医疗保健支付软件制造商 Waystar Holding Corp. 正考虑将其首次公开募股的定价定在其营销范围的中点附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/eqt-backed-waystar-is-said-to-weigh-pricing-ipo-around-mid-range</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 18:15:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Authentic Brands 利用贷款市场削减成本并筹集收购资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/authentic-brands-taps-loan-market-to-slash-costs-fund-buyout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Authentic Brands Group 正寻求削减 33 亿美元贷款的利息成本，并额外借入 4 亿美元用于收购，这是最新一家利用高风险债务接受市场获利的公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/authentic-brands-taps-loan-market-to-slash-costs-fund-buyout</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 18:07:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赫兹考虑出售价值 7 亿美元的担保债务和可转换债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/hertz-weighs-700-million-sale-of-secured-debt-plus-convertibles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，赫兹全球控股公司 (Hertz Global Holdings Inc.) 在遭遇电动汽车失误后寻求增强资产负债表，正在考虑出售至少 7 亿美元的担保债务以及发行可转换票据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/hertz-weighs-700-million-sale-of-secured-debt-plus-convertibles</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 18:04:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券持有人就瑞士信贷 AT1 债券在美国起诉瑞士</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/bondholders-sue-switzerland-in-us-over-credit-suisse-at1-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在瑞银集团通过瑞士政府斡旋的交易拯救瑞士信贷集团后，该集团债券的投资者损失惨重，他们正在美国法院起诉这个欧洲国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/bondholders-sue-switzerland-in-us-over-credit-suisse-at1-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 17:33:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交通谈判陷入僵局，多伦多准备罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/toronto-commuters-brace-for-friday-strike-as-transit-talks-stall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多伦多市政府与工会交通运输工人之间的劳资谈判在罢工前数小时陷入僵局，此次罢工有可能扰乱加拿大人口最多的城市 150 多万通勤者的生活。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/toronto-commuters-brace-for-friday-strike-as-transit-talks-stall</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 17:26:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
